  &lt;p&gt;&lt;a href=&quot;http://www.appleinsider.com/articles/11/04/22/inside_mac_os_x_10_7_lion_preview_office_file_viewing_new_text_and_signature_annotation.html&quot;&gt;Mac OS X 10.7 Lion to add Office file viewing, new text and signature annotation&lt;/a&gt;&lt;/p&gt; 
  &lt;p&gt;&lt;a href=&quot;http://www.appleinsider.com/articles/11/04/14/mac_os_x_10_7_lion_new_multitouch_gestures_dock_integration_for_expos_launchpad_mission_control.html&quot;&gt;Mac OS X 10.7 Lion: new multitouch gestures, Dock integration for Expos�, Launchpad, Mission Control&lt;/a&gt;&lt;/p&gt; 
